        "timestamp": "2020-10-30 09:53:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nDears,\n\nAs discussed in the TSC call yesterday, the so-ve-vnfm-adapter is depreciated.\nWe cannot really see any new released images for it in the SO project for Guilin.\n\nAs we have issues with total SO Helm chart size, I would propose to remove this chart completely.\nWe had some gating runs already, where we were using a non-existing so-ve-vnfm-adapter image (and so-ve-vnfm-adapter was not installing properly), and this had not impact on gating tests.\n\nI`ll need Your +1s to agree, that we remove that chart in Guilin and going forward.\nPlease add additional reviewers, if needed.\n\nRgds,\nDamian",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
